(136, 60, 1, 'admin', 'The energy-saving magnet independently developed the closed-loop function 10T100mm high-field refrigerator directly cool', '', '', '', '0', 'Recently, the 10T100mm chiller with closed-loop operation function independently developed by Xi''an Jueneng Superconducting Magnet Technology Co., Ltd., which was independently dev...', '<p>\r\n	Recently, the 10T100mm chiller with closed-loop operation function independently developed by Xi''an Jueneng Superconducting Magnet Technology Co., Ltd., which was independently developed by the Western Superconductor Company, successfully cooled the liquid-free 氦 superconducting magnet, and all technical indicators were better than the design value. The minimum temperature of the magnet is 3.4k, which fills the domestic gap. This is the first time to realize the zero-resistance closed-loop operation of NbTi and Nb3Sn hybrid superconducting magnets after 2T84, 3.6T160, 6T84, 8T100, 10T100, 13T40 and other open-loop running cryogenic magnets, marking the company''s high-field super-flow in the liquid-free field. Another major leap in the field of magnetizing design and manufacturing.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="/en/Uploads/201808/5b83b48258652.jpg" width="600" height="450" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:left;">\r\n	Since the superconducting magnet needs to be powered by the superconducting power supply, once the power supply problem occurs, the magnetic field of the magnet disappears immediately and the field changing operation occurs at the same time. However, if the power supply is disconnected in the steady magnetic field application, that is, the closed-loop mode operation can not only reduce the operating cost of the magnet, but also avoid the quenching or damage of the magnet caused by the magnet power problem. However, due to the fact that the key technology of constant current mode switching applied to the direct cooling of chillers has not been broken in China, the special low-temperature superconducting wire for the switch has long relied on imports, and the technology of magnet manufacturing technology using this mode has been restricted. In China, scientific research and industrial use are not available. Liquid helium high field magnets have not been able to achieve closed-loop mode operation for a long time, which severely restricts the popularization and application of superconducting magnets and seriously hinders the industrial development and technological progress in the above key areas.<br />\r\nAfter a six-month joint research, Superconductor Co., Ltd. of Western Superconductor Co., Ltd. broke through the "preparation of superconducting wire for PCS", "design and manufacture of direct cooling PCS for chiller" and "refrigerator" for the first time in China. A number of core key technologies, such as direct cooling magnet closed-loop technology, eliminate the dependence of equipment on liquid helium resources and power supply, and save a lot of operating costs for scientific research and industrial manufacturing users. In the future, the company will take this opportunity to continue to accelerate the application of high-performance superconducting magnets to meet the urgent needs of domestic and foreign customers.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:left;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="http://47.95.110.189:8080/Uploads/201808/5b8375f2b07d5.jpg" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '/en/Uploads/201808/5b83b48258652.jpg', 0, 1, 1, '', 0, 0, '/en/index.php?m=Article&a=show&id=136', 0, 1535358180, 1535359819, '', 0, ''),
(137, 60, 1, 'admin', 'Wang Hong, the western superconductor company, won the &quot;Outstanding Contribution Award&quot; from Double Airways', '', '', '', '0', 'Recently, Wang Hong, a forging operator of the No. 2 Manufacturing Plant of Western Superconductor, was awarded the “Outstanding Contribution Award” by Wanhang Die Forging Co., L...', '<p>\r\n	Recently, Wang Hong, a forging operator of the No. 2 Manufacturing Plant of Western Superconductor, was awarded the “Outstanding Contribution Award” by Wanhang Die Forging Co., Ltd. of the Second Heavy Machinery Group, in recognition of the company’s large-scale complex of A-100 steel for aircraft landing gear. Outstanding contribution in the development of die forgings.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="http://47.95.110.189:8080/Uploads/201808/5b8376743a8fd.jpg" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:left;">\r\n	&nbsp;In 2016, Double Wang &nbsp;Hong entrusted the company to carry out trial production of special-shaped parts for the project. After accepting the forging task, the main operator Wang Hong exchanged and cooperated with the technicians, independently developed the operation plan and control points for the special-shaped parts of the project, broke through a number of key technical bottlenecks, ensured the material delivery, and made rapid progress of the project. Research provides strong support. Received a high rating from the user.\r\n</p>', '', 'http://47.95.110.189:8080/Uploads/201808/5b8376743a8fd.jpg', 0, 1, 1, '', 0, 0, '/en/index.php?m=Article&a=show&id=137', 0, 1535358473, 1535359880, '', 0, ''),
(138, 60, 1, 'admin', 'Western Superconductor Company provides a donation to poor areas in Zhashui County', '', '', '', '0', 'At the beginning of 2018, Western Superconductor Company responded to the national “Participation in Poverty Alleviation and Development and Implementing Poverty Alleviation” to provide a donation o...', '<p>\r\n	At the beginning of 2018, Western Superconductor Company responded to the national “Participation in Poverty Alleviation and Development and Implementing Poverty Alleviation” to provide a donation of RMB 120,000 to Wafangkou Town, Zhashui County, Shangluo City for road construction in the town. On August 20th, Xia Baotian, chairman of the Wafangkou Town People''s Congress, made a special trip to the company to express their sincere gratitude to the people in the donor area for their love behavior and to give a thank you card. General Manager of the company, Party Secretary Feng Yong, Deputy Secretary of the Party Branch Li Yiyuan, and Chairman of the Labor Union Luo Jinhua received the visitors.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="http://47.95.110.189:8080/Uploads/201808/5b837730bf805.jpg" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:left;">\r\n	Wafangkou Town, Zhashui County is located in the Qinling Mountains, and its economic development is relatively lagging behind. In the process of developing poverty alleviation industry in the town, road construction faces a difficult situation of serious shortage of funds. After learning of this situation, the company actively provided the town with much-needed funds for the laying of cement roads to help the construction of the project be completed as scheduled. The townsmen of the town bid farewell to the dusty yellow mud road and embarked on the development of characteristic industries. A new journey to change the face of poverty.<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;In the meeting, General Manager Feng Yong said that the Western Superconductor will continue to adhere to the corporate tenet of "serving the country and benefiting mankind" and firmly practice the corporate responsibility of "not forgetting the original heart and giving back to the society", and the tile house in Lishui County. The town will strengthen exchanges and cooperation in the future, hoping to do its utmost for the region to get rid of poverty and develop.\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="http://47.95.110.189:8080/Uploads/201808/5b83777bbc5e3.jpg" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', 'http://47.95.110.189:8080/Uploads/201808/5b837730bf805.jpg', 0, 1, 1, '', 0, 0, '/en/index.php?m=Article&a=show&id=138', 3, 1535358696, 1535359927, '', 0, ''),
(139, 61, 1, 'admin', 'Technology advantages accelerate to high-end', '', '', '', '0', 'Just as the C919 aircraft was officially offline, the Western Superconductor announced a second fixed increase plan. The company intends to issue 50 million shares of stock at a price not less than 15...', 'Just as the C919 aircraft was officially offline, the Western Superconductor announced a second fixed increase plan. The company intends to issue 50 million shares of stock at a price not less than 15 yuan / share, 20 yuan / share, and raise 1 billion yuan for special aviation titanium alloy expansion and technical renovation projects.<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Western Superconductor said that in the next few years, with the batch production of new fighter aircraft, large aircraft, engines, helicopters and other types of projects, the company''s special aviation titanium alloy production capacity can not meet the needs of aviation customers, the fund-raising will promote the company''s business growth in this field.\r\n</p>\r\nIt is reported that the company plans to build three new smelting, rapid forging and continuous rolling workshops and add more than 60 sets of international advanced special titanium alloy ingot and bar production equipment in the project of capacity expansion of special titanium alloy materials for aviation. The total investment of the project is 650 million yuan.<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	In July, Western Superconductor completed a 15 yuan per share, a total of 225 million yuan of additional issuance, a total of 22 institutional investors subscribed for the additional shares (including three market makers).\r\n</p>\r\nIt is understood that the Western superconducting fund-raising of 225 million yuan will be mainly used for nickel based superalloy projects. According to Xingye Securities Research Report, nickel-based superalloys are generally used to make structural parts such as turbine discs and blades for aerospace engines. At present, these materials are purchased from abroad in China. Western superconductors have been reserved and accumulated in nickel-based superalloys and other fields for many years. At present, the company has the foundation and external conditions for industrialization.<br />', '', '/en/Uploads/201808/5b83b8d06f2c3.jpg', 0, 1, 1, '', 0, 0, '/en/index.php?m=Article&a=show&id=139', 0, 1535359228, 1535359228, '', 0, ''),
(140, 61, 1, 'admin', '&quot;Chinas man-made solar device to create a new world record&quot; was the ten major scientific and technological pro', '', '', '', '0', 'On December 31, 2017, the top 10 scientific and technological developments in China in 2017 were announced by members of the Chinese Academy of Sciences and the Chinese Academy of Engineering. The new...', 'On December 31, 2017, the top 10 scientific and technological developments in China in 2017 were announced by members of the Chinese Academy of Sciences and the Chinese Academy of Engineering. The news of stable 101.2 second steady-state long-pulse high-confinement mode plasma operation by EAST was reported. The "new world record set by China''s artificial solar device" was listed.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTen major scientific and technological progress news selection<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe annual award was sponsored by the Chinese Academy of Sciences and the Chinese Academy of Engineering, and organized by the Work Bureau of the Chinese Academy of Sciences, the General Office of the Chinese Academy of Engineering and the Chinese Science Journal. The judges are members of the Chinese Academy of Sciences and the Chinese Academy of Engineering, and have been held 24 times so far.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChina''s top ten scientific and technological progress news in 2017<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChinese scientists use chemical substances to synthesize intact active chromosomes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChina''s underwater glider refreshed the world record 6329 meters below the surface.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe birth of the world''s first optical quantum computer beyond the early classical computer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChina made large aircraft C919 "first flight"<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChina''s first sea area gas hydrate test production<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChina''s "artificial sun" device creates a new world record.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChinese scientists first discovered breakthroughs in traditional classification of new fermions<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQuantum communication "from the ideal kingdom to the real kingdom"<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Chinese Academy of Sciences has introduced a new high yield rice germplasm.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChina''s dark matter particle detection satellite "Wukong" found suspected dark matter traces.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe following is from the China Science Journal.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Oriental Superconducting Ring (EAST), a national large scientific device, has achieved stable 101.2 second long pulse high confinement plasma operation and set a new world record. This important breakthrough marks that China''s magnetic confinement fusion research will continue to lead the international frontier in physics and engineering aspects of steady-state operation. Oriental Supercycle is the first Tokamak nuclear fusion experimental facility in the world to operate in a steady-state high-constraint mode for a duration of 100 seconds. It is of great scientific significance to the International Thermonuclear Fusion Test Reactor (ITER) program. Because the reaction mechanism of nuclear fusion is similar to that of the sun, the Oriental Supercycle is also known as the "artificial sun". The results will provide important scientific and experimental support for the long pulse and high constraint operation of ITER in the future, and lay a foundation for the research, construction, operation and personnel training of the next generation fusion device, China Fusion Engineering Experimental Reactor.<br />', '', '/Uploads/201808/5b6dab7aefa78.jpg', 0, 1, 1, '', 0, 0, '/en/index.php?m=Article&a=show&id=140', 2, 1535359344, 1535359344, '', 0, ''),
(141, 62, 1, 'admin', 'The first component of ITER large superconducting magnet system was developed successfully.', '', '', '', '0', 'The reporter learned from the Chinese Academy of Sciences that ITER, an international major scientific project jointly undertaken by China, the United States, Japan, Russia, the European Union, South ...', 'The reporter learned from the Chinese Academy of Sciences that ITER, an international major scientific project jointly undertaken by China, the United States, Japan, Russia, the European Union, South Korea and India, is the largest international cooperation organization in the world at present, and ITER is also a key step to realize commercial fusion energy in the future. On the morning of July 26, the first part of ITER superconducting magnet system was successfully developed by the Institute of Plasma, Hefei Research Institute, Chinese Academy of Sciences.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe magnet feeder system is one of the most complex systems in ITER components, including 31 sets of different feeders, each with a length of 30-50 meters and a total weight of more than 1600 tons, totaling more than 60,000 parts. It is the key integrated channel for power supply, cooling and diagnostic signal of ITER superconducting magnet system. It is called the lifeline of ITER host. The project undertakers have overcome many technical difficulties and achieved many international leading achievements in the core technologies of HTS current leads, superconducting connectors, low temperature insulation, low temperature and high voltage insulation. The Wan''an high-temperature superconducting current lead, which combines the advantages of high current carrying capacity, low cooling consumption and long cooling loss safety time, replaces the original ITER copper current lead design proposed by Japan and other developed countries, and greatly reduces the operation cost of ITER and the construction investment of cryogenic system. The 68 kA high temperature superconducting current lead has set a world record of running at 85 kA for one hour and 90 kA for four minutes. The developed box-type high current-carrying and low-loss superconducting connector has a world-leading resistance of 0.2 nano-Euro, which greatly ensures the safe operation of the main engine of ITER device.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 2006, China formally participated in the ITER program, with 10% input to 100% of intellectual property rights, striving to absorb and digest the United States, Russia and other countries in the shortest time decades of research results. Following the establishment of the world''s first fully superconducting Tokamak nuclear fusion experimental facility EAST, the Institute of Plasma Physics has put forward the best scheme on ITER superconducting magnet feeder system and ITER large-scale power supply project, which has been adopted by international organizations and created in China, not only eliminating the future operational risk of ITER. It also shows our leading technology level in the world. Our ITER mission 100% localization and excellent performance indicators through international evaluation, product quality 100% to meet the requirements of ITER, the first delivery of seven ITER site, progress in the seven participating countries in the forefront, creating a number of first.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe two director general of the ITER group commented that "China is ahead of all parties in the procurement package development." In addition, with our advanced R&amp;D and quality standards, some of the key systems and components in the other side''s share (e.g. 400 tons of EU large superconducting magnets) have to be subcontracted to us through international bidding. At the same time, the fusion plants of France, Germany and the United States have sought me several times in the course of development and upgrading. The help of key technologies in national fusion project requires us to develop components. We have mastered the core fusion technology and achieved the export of key technologies.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThrough undertaking the national large-scale scientific project and participating in ITER project, China independently develops key Fusion Engineering technology, realizes many Chinese inventions in the unceasing innovation, fills the international blank, and forms the bureau which our country occupies 60% of the international market share in the field of low-temperature superconducting materials and 100% of the high-temperature superconducting current leads are completely provided by me. It has been widely applied in industry and promoted the vigorous development of high-tech enterprises in China. The technology and components of superconducting materials, cryogenic materials and high-power power power supply devices have been developed from scratch to large-scale production and exported to western developed countries. Our country has mastered the key technology of fusion engineering, which is irreplaceable on the international fusion stage, and will make more contributions to mankind.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNuclear fusion energy is considered as one of the most promising energy sources in the future because of its cleanliness, environmental protection, safety and rich raw materials. China''s controllable nuclear fusion research began in the early 1960s, under the guidance of the national innovation-driven development strategy and the overall goal of building a world scientific and technological power, through the construction of the "11th Five-Year Plan" and the "12th Five-Year Plan" of the national fusion project and the accumulation of the participation of the international large scientific plan, to the present "13th Five-Year Plan" early stage, I The key technology of China''s nuclear fusion project is based on independent innovation, from the 1990s to today''s real lead.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe niobium titanium superconducting wire in the magnet system is supplied by the Western superconductor company.<br />', '', '/en/Uploads/201808/5b83b9b214ec9.jpg', 0, 1, 1, '', 0, 0, '/en/index.php?m=Article&a=show&id=141', 1, 1535359454, 1535359454, '', 0, ''),
(142, 62, 1, 'admin', 'Research and development of the key technology of the superconducting DC fault current limiter by the Western supercondu', '', '', '', '0', 'With the development of China''s national economy, the capacity and scale of the power system continue to expand, and the short-circuit faults of the power grid frequently occur, which has already had ...', 'With the development of China''s national economy, the capacity and scale of the power system continue to expand, and the short-circuit faults of the power grid frequently occur, which has already had a certain impact on the operational safety and power supply reliability of the State Grid. With the rapid development of high-temperature superconducting materials application technology, high-temperature superconducting resistor type current limiter has been highly concerned by power fields in various countries in recent years due to its simple structure, obvious current limiting effect and fast response speed. .<br />\r\nThe “Key Technology Research of Superconducting DC Current Limiter”, “Smart Grid Technology and Equipment”, led by China Southern Power Grid Guangdong Power Grid Co., Ltd., was established in July 2017. The project is aimed at the actual application of the power grid, and will complete the world''s first high-voltage class DC current limiter and realize the hanging network in the Guangdong Nanao ±160 kV multi-terminal flexible DC transmission demonstration project.<br />\r\nAmong them, the company is responsible for the design and manufacture of superconducting DC current regulator cryogenic vessels, cryogenic refrigeration systems, and low temperature high voltage outlet units as sub-projects of the sub-project "Design and manufacture of cryogenic systems and high-voltage outlet units". The differential pressure driven forced flow cooling device will be developed for the first time in the world to comprehensively improve the fault response and recovery capability of the resistive DC current limiter.<br />\r\nAfter the completion of the project, the key technical problems faced by the resistor-type high-temperature superconducting current limiter in the flexible DC transmission grid application will be solved in one fell swoop, and the operational safety of the grid will be improved comprehensively. The application of the superconducting current limiter in the future power grid will be Important theoretical and engineering guidance, the market has broad prospects.<br />', '', '/en/Uploads/201808/5b83ba1cdb8b0.jpg', 0, 1, 1, '', 0, 0, '/en/index.php?m=Article&a=show&id=142', 2, 1535359546, 1535359562, '', 0, '');
