(56, '公司简介', '', '', '', 'Xi''an Jueneng Superconducting Magnet Technology Co., Ltd. was established in 2011. It is a holding subsidiary of Western Superconducting Materials Technology Co., Ltd., and Western Superconducting Materials Technology Co., Ltd. has the production capacity of NbTi and Nb3Sn/Cu, while Xi''an Ju Neng Superconducting Magnet Technology Co., Ltd. has complete R&amp;D and manufacturing capabilities for superconducting magnets.<br />\r\nSince 2009, Western Superconductor has cooperated with the internationally renowned superconducting magnet manufacturer Japan Superconducting Technology Co., Ltd. (JASTEC) to break through and form a completely independent intellectual property right Ф300mm MCZ super through the introduction of digestion and absorption and innovation. Guide magnet preparation technology. In 2010, Western Superconductor dispatched a technical team of 20 people to the JASTEC production line in Japan to manufacture a 超300mm MCZ monocrystalline silicon manufacturing superconducting magnet. The magnet has been supplied to the world''s largest single crystal silicon manufacturer - Shin-Etsu Chemical Co., Ltd. And applied to the manufacture of Ф300mm monocrystalline silicon. In 2013, the company began an in-depth cooperation with the Lanzhou Institute of Modern Physics to develop and manufacture superconducting magnets for accelerators. In 2015, it successfully produced 81 9T superconducting magnets for the US FRIB project.<br />\r\nAt present, the company has more than 40 professional R &amp; D personnel such as doctors and masters. The professional direction involves physics, electronics, machinery, low temperature, superconductivity, vacuum, etc., forming a professional R&amp;D team for superconducting magnet technology. A total of 21 sets of main equipment related to magnet production have been put into production. At present, a complete production line for magnet production has been formed, which can produce various types of large superconducting magnets with a diameter of up to 2 m. It is currently the largest magnet production equipment in China.<br />\r\nAs of October 2016, Xi''an Jueneng Superconducting Magnet Technology Co., Ltd. has carried out more than 30 kinds (110 sets) of low-temperature, high-temperature superconducting magnets and system design, processing and production, including the Institute of Modern Physics of the Chinese Academy of Sciences, Lanzhou Branch Taiji New Technology Co., Ltd., Peking University, Southwest Institute of Physics of Nuclear Industry, Anhui Wanrui Cold Power Technology Co., Ltd., Chengdu University of Electronic Science and Technology and other units provide services and products, winning the praise of customers!<br />\r\n<br />', '', 0, ''),
